title: AMD_catalyst_11.6_early_preview_8.86_W7_Vista.7z
description:
very newest version from AMD
this version is supposed to definitively fix the recurent well known mouse lag
90 % positive feedback for the moment...
no release note yet as well...sorry !
This new driver have also a new direct3D,2D and openGL version.
Many thanks to our friend asder00 from guru3d for this very cool news :)
not official yet by AMD
Seems apparently a very very good driver...
Worth a download anyway
as i am still curently seeding sulmultaneously multi-torrents you might get
possible slow download...
I truly apologize for this inconvenience.
I will try to cap some of them if necessary to help you more.
this is the complete driver package for Vista/Win7 both version.
few mobility models are supported also.
I suggest you on Vista to install by manual method directly by device manager itself after having extracted the archieve anywhere on your computer so.
By now,let's see more details about this new driver :
